snippet.description:

However, India soon struck back and took six wickets which ended day 4 with Bangladesh on 272 runs. India needs just 4 wickets on the final day whereas Bangladesh needs a massive 241 runs for victory.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Gruha Pravesam || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Gruha Pravesam MCM

In this new Middle Class Madhu episode, Madhu strikes up a humorous chat with the milkman and her father arrives bearing a grocery list for a special occasion. When Madhu arrives with the supplies from Budatha's store, he realises that the event is their new home's opening. Madhu urges Mahesh to make elaborate arrangements for the newly built house in her happiness. Mahesh, Balli, and Budatha set up everything in front of the new house, but they eventually realise that the property belongs to the manager and not the madhus. Have a lovely weekend and watch the new video Gruhapravesam's(HOUSE WARMING) humorous conclusion.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3644 - 17 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3644: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide's mama has reached Gokuldham society with many people in tow in his search for Popatlal. When everyone sees the group, they get scared for Bhide and Popatlal. Bhide and his family rush down to meet him and Bhide's friends follow him. As soon as he gets to the society compound they form a circle around his family to protect them. But Bhide wants to apologize to his mama and he tries to make him understand that he is innocent in all this. Will his mama listen?

Show Name â€“ Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast â€“  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3644, 17 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: WOH (Official Video) - Ikka x Dino James x Badshah | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
Indiaâ€™s Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on â€˜Woh.â€™ The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. â€˜Wohâ€™ is one of the very few records which portray a manâ€™s emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshahâ€™s verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. â€˜Wohâ€™ is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

snippet.title: Garden Update Vlog in Tamil | Nesting Box for Coco | Preparing Plants for Winter and harvest Vlog
snippet.description:
In this video join me as we prepare the plants for the upcoming cold winter. We harvested banana, sugarcane, orange and some raspberries. We also made a nesting box for coco so that they will be warm during the winter. We also made some mini greenhouse for the tropical plants. Our passionfruit plant also flowered for the first time.
#gardenupdate #homegarden #steffigarden

Friends, hope you liked this week's vlog, see you next week with more interesting videos.

snippet.title: 1st Test - Day 1 | Hindi | Key Moments | India Tour Of Bangladesh | 14th December 2022
snippet.description:
In the 1st Test match, India won the toss and elected to bat first. Both the openers were dismissed quickly but next up was Cheteshwar Pujara, who played a solid knock of 90 runs. Later, Shreyas Iyer joined the party by scoring an unbeaten 82. India ended up with 278 runs at the end of day 1 but lost 6 wickets in the process.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3643 - 16 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3643: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide eventually calls Bagha and Nattu Kaka as part of his ongoing quest for Popatlal. Bagha and Nattu Kaka are peppered with inquiries. To confirm their honesty on Popatlal, Bhide even asks them to make a vow before God. Popatlal is being sought frantically by everyone in Gokuldham, but he appears to have vanished mysteriously. Madhavi and Sonu also are saddened by Bhide's anxieties as he feels bad for hurting his uncle. Watch the episode

Show Name â€“ Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast â€“  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3643, 16 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #à¤¤à¤¾à¤°à¤•à¤®à¥‡à¤¹à¤¤à¤¾à¤•à¤¾à¤‰à¤²à¥à¤Ÿà¤¾à¤šà¤¶à¥à¤®à¤¾ #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.description:
Jaadu ya chamatkaar? Dhoka ya yaqeen? Vardaan ya shraap? 
Dekho Vasya ki anokhi kahani Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar mein, all episodes streaming from Jan 6th, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstarâ€™s upcoming fantasy-drama series, Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar explores just this with the one of Indiaâ€™s most beloved content creator, Bhuvan Bam in the lead. Set in Mumbai, this one-of-a-kind uplifting series will take viewers on a riveting ride of a man stumbling upon a miracle and the ripples it creates in his humble life. 

The series is being directed by Himank Gaur who previously directed Dhindora and is produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under the banner of BB Ki Vines Productions. The show has been penned by powerful writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal and also stars Shriya Pilgaonkar, JD Chakravarthy, Deven Bhojani, Prathmesh Parab, Shilpa Shukla, Mahesh Manjarekar and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.
 
Based on the life of a sanitation worker, the series light-heartedly depicts class-based poverty and the human desire to lead a better life. The Hotstar Specials series marks Bhuvan Bamâ€™s first association with a streaming platform and will see him in an all-new fictional role.

à¤¦à¥à¤°à¥Œà¤ªà¤¦à¥€ à¤¨à¥‡ à¤•à¤°à¥à¤£ à¤¸à¥‡ à¤µà¤¿à¤µà¤¾à¤¹ à¤•à¥à¤¯à¥‹à¤‚ à¤¨à¤¹à¥€à¤‚ à¤•à¤¿à¤¯à¤¾ à¤¥à¤¾? | Mahabharat Best Scene | B R Chopra | Pen Bhakti

Without pause or hesitation Arjun shoots his arrow into the target. He wins Draupadiâ€™s hand in marriage. The princes are loud with anger. â€œHow can a Brahmin marry a princess?â€ they demand. A fight seems imminent. Shri Krishna seeks to appease the princes and Arjun and Bheem protect Draupadi. At long lost they take Draupadi to their temporary abode. Kunti unknowingly asks the five Pandava brothers to share their bride prize. Also, Shri Krishna meets his aunt Kunti and his cousins. Siyani Episode 126 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 17th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle by mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiranâ€™s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughterâ€™s nature and doesnâ€™t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiranâ€™s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams until she comes across Zohaib who turns out to be her only well-wisher.

After meeting Zohaib, will Ujala ever find the love and respect she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

snippet.title: 3 BIG FISH FRY | Streaked Spanish Mackerel Fish Fry Recipe Cooking In Village Vanjaram Meen Varuval
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook three big fish fry recipe. We call this fish as vanjaram in our village. We cutting the fish slice and marinate the slices with traditional hand-ground masala. Then we fried it in traditionally made gingelly oil.

Finally, we taste this fish fry recipe with our favorite mutton curry.

Yummy!

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Argentina 3:0 Croatia - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Argentina booked their place in the Final with a 3-0 win over Croatia at the Lusail Stadium.

Quickfire first-half goals by Lionel Messi, from the penalty spot & then from Julian Alvarez, following a darting run from his own half, put the Albiceleste in control of the contest.

The pair were at it in the second half again with Messi, after a darting run, setting up an easy tap-in for Alvarez; thus confirming a sixth #FIFAWorldCup Final appearance for the Albiceleste.

Lionel Scaloni's side will face defending champions France or surprise package Morocco in the summit clash on Sunday - Dec 18.

Enjoy the highlights of #ARGCRO & keep watching the #WorldsGreatestShow on #JioCinema & #Sports18 ğŸ“ºğŸ“²

*About* 
------------

Yeh prem kahani hai Delhi ke business tycoon, Arnav Raizada aur Lucknow ke middle class ladki, Khushi ki. Ek taraf ghamandi Arnav aur doosri taraf chulbuli Khushi, dono hi ek doosre se bilkul alag. Arnav aur Khushi baar baar takraye aur shuru hogai unke beech pyaari nok zhok. 
Apni badi behen Anjali ki shaadi bachane ke liye, Arnav ne ki Khushi se shaadi. Waqt ke sath sath, Arnav aur Khushi ka rishta hogaya mazboot. Anchaha rishta badal gaya umra bhar ke pyaar mai. Khushi ne haasil ki apni nayi pehchaan. Arnav-Khushi ko mila apna happily ever after.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3642 - 15 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3642: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide queries Gogi about Popatlal's location after learning that he has been hiding at Sodhi's house. Bhide begins to question Gogi when he responds to him because of his stutter. Their covert lies make Taarak and Anjali nervous. Sodhi queries Bhide as to the reason behind his frantic hunt for Popatlal. Bhide describes how Popatlal met Vidya, his cousin, in secret. Later, Bhide requests help from the entire Gokuldham society in finding Popatlal. Watch the episode

Show Name â€“ Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast â€“  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3642, 15 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: 3rd ODI | Key Moments | India Tour Of Bangladesh | 10th December 2022
snippet.description:
In the 3rd ODI, India was simply brilliant with the bat. Ishan Kishan led the side with a record-breaking double century whereas Virat Kohli scored his 72nd ton to help India reach 409 runs. Bangladesh never looked like chasing down the total as they lost wickets at crucial intervals. India ended a superb ODI series with a sizzling 227 run victory.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - France 2:0 Morocco - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
France became the first team since 1998 to stand a chance of defending their #FIFAWorldCup crown with a 2-0 win over Morocco. 

Theo Hernandez fired Les Bleus ahead in the 5th minute with an acrobatic strike. This was the first time an opposition player scored against the North Africans in #Qatar2022. The Moroccan attack tested Hugo Lloris but were unlucky to not be level. Meanwhile, Olivier Giroud could not convert two opportunities to seal the result in favour of Didier Deschamps' side.

Substitute Randal Kolo Muani scored the second of the night for the defending champions with his first touch of the ball in the 79th minute. With his first international goal, the Eintracht Frankfurt booked the dream date with Argentina & end Morocco's dream run at the #WorldsGreatestShow.

Relive the best moments from #FRAMAR and stay tuned to #JioCinema & #Sports18  to find out which nation becomes the World Champion ğŸ“ºğŸ“²

Siyani Episode 124 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 15th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle by mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiranâ€™s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughterâ€™s nature and doesnâ€™t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiranâ€™s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams until she comes across Zohaib who turns out to be her only well-wisher.

After meeting Zohaib, will Ujala ever find the love and respect she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment
